types can contribute global explorers
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

__mein_type/
   global/
      explorer/
         status-von-foo
         anderer

$out/explorer/
   hostname
   os
   ...
   __mein_type/
      status-von-foo
      anderer


todos:
- cdist scans types for global/explorer's
- when executing explorers, create the types namespace folder before running type gobal explorers

